title: Women’s Soccer Battles into Overtime, Drops 1-0 loss to Grove City (Geneva College)
text: ( Source : Geneva College ) Beaver Falls, PA - Geneva hosted Grove City under the lights at Reeves Field Friday to open Presidents' Athletic Conference play. The Golden Tornadoes took Grove City into overtime but fell in the 97th minute, 1-0.
